MarketTool interface;

Stock, Bond and Option concrete class to implement this interface;

Currency interface;

Rmb, Usd and Hkd concrete class to implement this interface;

AbstractFactory abstract class have two methods, getCurrencyValue and getMarketValue;

CurrencyFactory class extends AbstractFactory

MarketFactory class extends AbstractFactory

FactoryProducer decides which factory to build. Use FactoryProducer to build different factories and build different objects



